Thank you for downloading!
==================

Okay, so the .bsp file contains 3 materials and 3 textures, as well as it contains 1 sound file.
Just letting you know, that there are some more things to explore.
To install just simply move the fy_manhunt.bsp file to your Steam\steamapps\username\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps directory.
Please, tell me if you're missing any textures, there should be no problem, but tell me if you encounter any missing textures or sound.
